The final episode of Game of Thrones airs tomorrow morning at 3am. Season eight has been a hot topic of discussion around the world. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG – It is the last-ever episode of epic TV series Game of Thrones and fans are in a frenzy. The final episode will air at 3am South African time on Monday. While many say they will stay up and watch, others are concerned the final offering might not live up to its hype. READ: Robert Pattinson will be the next Batman - reports Some fans have gone as far as signing a petition for creators to remake season eight, saying it felt rushed. Local fans gave their opinion on how they feel about the end and which character they best identify. The final episode of Game of Thrones airs on Monday morning at 3am. Courtesy #DStv403